3. Allow the conversion of multiple files at once
  3.1 Create a list of files on UI
  3.2 Convert files one at a time down the list
  3.3 Convert all button or individual convert button
  3.4 Download all or individual download button
  3.4 Cancel conversion button, finishes current then stops

